'''Qhorin''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by [[Simon Armstrong]]. Qhorin Halfhand is a member of the [[Night's Watch]], a senior and experienced ranger who is regarded as an elite scout and soldier. He is known as '''Qhorin Halfhand''' or simply '''The Halfhand'''.

